import requests, json
# fetch and print dataset cell_type term IDs for the 2 deployments
info={
    '21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde': ('ed9185e3-5b82-40c7-9824-b2141590c7f0', 'e6ef9f09-bf7f-49bf-900c-457c02675411'),
    '0b75c598-0893-4216-afe8-5414cab7739d': ('bcb61471-2a44-4d00-a0af-ff085512674c', '25b62707-5933-415b-8000-3369ec4af23f'),
}
for dep_id,(cid, dsid) in info.items():
    col=requests.get(f'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/collections/{cid}', timeout=20).json()
    ds=[d for d in col['datasets'] if d['id']==dsid][0]
    cell_types=[x['ontology_term_id'] for x in ds.get('cell_type',[])]
    tissues=[x['ontology_term_id'] for x in ds.get('tissue',[])]
    print(dep_id, 'dataset name', ds.get('name'))
    print('n cell_types', len(cell_types), 'unique', len(set(cell_types)))
    print('first 10 cell_types', cell_types[:10])
    print('tissue terms', tissues)
